SUMMARY:Interchange Message: CAMDEN ROAD STATION: Until summer 2026\, no 
 step-free access to/from the eastbound platform. To start a step-free 
 eastbound journey\, take bus 274 to Caledonian Road & Barnsbury.\nTo 
 complete an eastbound step-free journey at Camden Road\, continue to 
 Caledonian Road & Barnsbury and change there to a westbound train.
END:VEVENT
